{{APIEntry|
|type=function
|name=required
|cat=Plugins/Validation/Methods
|return=Boolean
|desc=Makes then element always required.
|longdesc=Return false if the element is empty (text input) or unchecked (radio/checkbxo) or nothing selected (select).

Works with all kind of text inputs, selects, checkboxes and radio buttons.

<nowiki>To force a user to select an option from a select box, provide an empty options like <option value="">Choose...</option></nowiki>
|arg0=param
|arg0type=Boolean
|arg0desc=A boolean "true" makes a field always required.
|arg0optional=true
}}

